@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
### Swap @baseUrl to your Render URL once deployed, e.g.:
### @baseUrl = https://contacts-api-xxxx.onrender.com

### Get all contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts

### Get a single contact by id (replace with a real _id from the GET all response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/6a5487c4dae43836ea278f1e

### Create a new contact
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "purple",
  "birthday": "1815-12-10"
}

### Update a contact (replace with a real _id)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/contacts/6a5487c4dae43836ea278f1e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada.lovelace@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "teal",
  "birthday": "1815-12-10"
}

### Delete a contact (replace with a real _id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contacts/6a5487c4dae43836ea278f1e
